{"id": "ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 149, "displayName": {"text": "MENSHO Walnut Creek", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xaFVGQnRSR1J0ZHpaaFowZFdRMFYxY1c5TlIxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We absolutely loved this place! The broth is rich, flavorful, and comforting. The pudding is my daughter’s favorite—smooth, creamy, and incredibly tasty. We’re already planning to come back next week. Great food, excellent service, and a very welcoming atmosphere. Highly recommended! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We absolutely loved this place! The broth is rich, flavorful, and comforting. The pudding is my daughter’s favorite—smooth, creamy, and incredibly tasty. We’re already planning to come back next week. Great food, excellent service, and a very welcoming atmosphere. Highly recommended! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "李倩", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117467917025857247648/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKG48oXLoGUH1MjSFAItroiCe80OE6VloVME4ws1yunmujejQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T04:42:57.029392323Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xaFVGQnRSR1J0ZHpaaFowZFdRMFYxY1c5TlIxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xaFVGQnRSR1J0ZHpaaFowZFdRMFYxY1c5TlIxRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085610077151769:0x3935d98110ba2ff5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoWFlTMDVjMmc1TWtNd2VEVklNV2xaVG0xNloxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place serves incredibly delicious and authentic ramen with a very unique menu that also creatively incorporates American culture. The interior design is stunning and eye-catching; walking inside truly feels like you’ve stepped right into Japan.\n\nThe staff is well-trained, full of energy, and provides excellent service. Although it’s on the pricier side, the high-quality food and the immersive dining experience make it well worth it. This is definitely my go-to spot whenever I’m craving and missing authentic Japanese ramen!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place serves incredibly delicious and authentic ramen with a very unique menu that also creatively incorporates American culture. The interior design is stunning and eye-catching; walking inside truly feels like you’ve stepped right into Japan.\n\nThe staff is well-trained, full of energy, and provides excellent service. Although it’s on the pricier side, the high-quality food and the immersive dining experience make it well worth it. This is definitely my go-to spot whenever I’m craving and missing authentic Japanese ramen!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Checheng Lin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112923187157141982999/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDxXIpdmf7m3qf-wJBimyGreC18FfbsAiZ8U4W__ebKLUN5T_t=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-15T16:24:32.612252281Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoWFlTMDVjMmc1TWtNd2VEVklNV2xaVG0xNloxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoWFlTMDVjMmc1TWtNd2VEVklNV2xaVG0xNloxRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085610077151769:0x3935d98110ba2ff5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xWFpWOXpYM2RpTTBGTGNVcG1URmRrUmsxVlFYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I've only tried the Menshonin San Francisco. I'm so happy they've opened one closer to where I live. Everything was delicious like I remember. They have vegan and vegetarian options as well as add one to your ramen. This is a must try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I've only tried the Menshonin San Francisco. I'm so happy they've opened one closer to where I live. Everything was delicious like I remember. They have vegan and vegetarian options as well as add one to your ramen. This is a must try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kennice Gary", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101794094997301322380/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNCanMRcQ9yUlf2nnaAoE4nAcKcKCebrsaopf7bOm0La1dvMNr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T19:16:23.262710419Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xWFpWOXpYM2RpTTBGTGNVcG1URmRrUmsxVlFYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xWFpWOXpYM2RpTTBGTGNVcG1URmRrUmsxVlFYYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085610077151769:0x3935d98110ba2ff5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xveVJ6ZHRPRzFaT1ZocmFIVjZNRFZ1UWxFellsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Happy they finally opened one in Walnut Creek! They have a ton of vegan options and the ramen is seriously some of the best around. The service was great, and I love how everyone welcomes you in Japanese when you walk in. The vibe and atmosphere are awesome too. Alex was our server - awesome recommendations. 👌 🍜", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Happy they finally opened one in Walnut Creek! They have a ton of vegan options and the ramen is seriously some of the best around. The service was great, and I love how everyone welcomes you in Japanese when you walk in. The vibe and atmosphere are awesome too. Alex was our server - awesome recommendations. 👌 🍜", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jimmy Wadhwa", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106038055947311040168/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2Civ83WWieBtUsXsjqSgmk-sg0n7ED5yh6E79Nqbihwbe1w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T04:49:21.892409999Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xveVJ6ZHRPRzFaT1ZocmFIVjZNRFZ1UWxFellsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xveVJ6ZHRPRzFaT1ZocmFIVjZNRFZ1UWxFellsRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085610077151769:0x3935d98110ba2ff5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOVVRFMXlRbTFrZVhsZlpqUldSME5KZVdkdVFtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "An awesome experience. Definitely some of the best ramen in the Bay Area, and I'm so happy it's finally closer to home.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "An awesome experience. Definitely some of the best ramen in the Bay Area, and I'm so happy it's finally closer to home.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Norah Yang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112314225209327080124/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZTc-gqfdekrqTkyL88mn61ygqWX2eKT3QXTKiBVAfYknD2Js=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T04:52:01.544124535Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOVVRFMXlRbTFrZVhsZlpqUldSME5KZVdkdVFtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOVVRFMXlRbTFrZVhsZlpqUldSME5KZVdkdVFtYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085610077151769:0x3935d98110ba2ff5"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJaRcVdwBhhYAR9S-6EIHZNTk/photos/AWCwydgnel1gqX8O58t5V879rQGUWayzFb1vJEJUrrR3_nZs5Y